    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, mechanically impeccable and finished in its original factory glaze. This specimen features the legendary S54 inline-six, exhibiting rock-solid oil pressure and a razor-sharp throttle response via its six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag six-speed manual engages with surgical precision, transmitting power through a perfectly dialed limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, with bushings and dampers offering the taut, communicative feedback these chassis are renowned for. A truly turnkey performance icon for the discerning purist.",
