      "description": "This vehicle is in truly impeccable, showroom condition, representing the pinnacle of automotive care. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish, free of even the slightest swirl marks or stone chips, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and regular professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time-capsule' state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and matte, with no signs of wear, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature and mechanical component functions with factory precision. This car has been exclusively serviced at the dealership with a comprehensive logbook to prove its pampered history. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a pre-owned vehicle that is indistinguishable from one on a showroom floor.",
