      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered, kept in a garage, and still has that fresh feel inside. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved to pieces and looks spectacular, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
