      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen is powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system that has been precisely calibrated for optimal valve timing. The high-revving valvetrain remains quiet and responsive, reflecting meticulous maintenance. The chassis is structurally pristine, having received proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The suspension retains its original kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the legendary handling characteristics are fully intact. A mechanically synchronized, museum-quality example for the serious driver.",
